data.description: Looking for the serenity of country living but want the conveniences of the city at your fingertips? Come see this immaculate, move-in 2400 sq ft home just minutes from Bolivar located in a quiet rural subdivision. This home has 4 large bedrooms - 2 upstairs/2 downstairs and 3 full baths. The master bedroom en suite has been completely renovated with updated tile, tub, walk-in shower, and vanity. You''ll find an efficiently designed kitchen with lots of storage, work space, breakfast bar, and space for a sizeable dining table. Adjacent to the kitchen is a living room (currently used as dining room) with French doors.
